TestTool.Model.TestTaking

Class TestTaking

  • java.lang.Object
    • TestTool.Model.TestTaking.TestTaking

  • public abstract class TestTaking
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is the main class for the package, this class handles all the utilities within the Test Taking UI. This class contains three variables, Question, LoginName, and TimeLimit to keep track of the basics of the test taking individual.
